===[[Pokémon Mezastar]]===
[[File:Lance Pokémon Mezastar.png|220px|thumb|Lance's promotional art for [[Pokémon Mezastar]]]]
Lance, in a version based on the animated series, appeared in [[Pokémon Mezastar]].<ref>https://twitter.com/Pokemon_Meza/status/1568434084275101696</ref> In this game, Lance is seen using a Shiny {{p|Gyarados}}, {{p|Dragonite}}, {{p|Lapras}}, and {{p|Hydreigon}}, with Lapras being a Pokémon that he has not been seen using in the animated series. In the [[Double Chain set 2 (Mezastar)|second Double Chain series set]], Lance also appeared as an opponent in an event that recreated the [[Masters Eight Tournament]] that ran from October 27 to November 21, 2022. Upon beating the character, the player can receive a Support Pokémon Ticket based on [[Lance's Gyarados]].<ref>https://pokemonmezastar.com/event/e2210142/</ref>

